nhc_headline: ...JERRY RACING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD ACROSS THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC...
summary: ...JERRY RACING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD ACROSS THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... As of 2:00 AM AST Wed Oct 08 the center of Jerry was located near 13.1, -49.8 with movement WNW at 23 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
